---
title: Crispy Serrano Ham and Charred Courgette Salad with Herby Roasted Potatoes, Croutons and Baby Leaves
description: Welcome the sunshine with our summery Crispy Serrano Ham and Charred Courgette Salad. Filled with fresh and vibrant produce, this salad is perfect for a lighter evening meal or to accompany a BBQ.
